    <section class="Welcome">
      <h1>Welcome to Rails Engine!</h1>
      <h3>Here is the documentation for all of our endpoints</h3>
      <p>Rails Engine is a backend e-commerce application providing fully tested API endpoints. The endpoints consist of information about merchants and their items as well as business logic enpoints providing statistical data about the merchant information located in our database.</p>
      <p>Please visit <a href="https://github.com/Kathybui732/rails_engine">Rails Engine</a> to view our github!</p>
    </section>

    <section class="Getting Started">
      <h3>Getting Started</h3>
      <p>The base URL for the application is <b>https://rails-engine-kb.herokuapp.com/api/v1</b></p>
      <p>Here are the following endpoints available from this application:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><b><pre><a href="#get-merchants">GET</a>, <a href="#post-merchants">POST</a> /merchants</b></li>
        <li><b><pre><a href="#get-merchants-id">GET</a>, <a href="#patch-merchants-id">PATCH</a>, <a href="#delete-merchants-id">DELETE</a> /merchants/:id</b></li>
